# ─── Vercel AI Gateway (default model path) ────────────────────────────────
# On Vercel, auth is handled automatically via OIDC — no env var needed.
# For local dev against the real Gateway, set this to your Vercel AI Gateway key:
# AI_GATEWAY_API_KEY=

# ─── Upstash Redis (rate limiting + lifetime free quota tracking) ──────────
# Install via: Vercel project → Storage → Marketplace → Upstash Redis
# The two vars below are injected automatically by the integration.
# UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=
# UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=
